<br>
It comes with the territory Biji.  Us silly gnome clerics not only lose out when it comes to wisdom (worst of all races for clerics) we also have pretty bad strength, and being a plate wearing class can often times find ourselves at max weight allowance with just our armor on.  At least we do good with stamina (and rockin' intelligence too, omg!!!).<br>
<br>
